---
const generatedAt = new Date().toISOString();
const instrumentationSnippet = `npm install @outlayo/sdk-ingest openai

import OpenAI from "openai";
import { setupPresetFetch } from "@outlayo/sdk-ingest";

const outlayo = setupPresetFetch({
  presets: [{ name: "openai" }]
});

const openai = new OpenAI({
  apiKey: process.env.OPENAI_API_KEY,
  fetch: outlayo.fetch
});

await openai.responses.create({
  model: "gpt-4o-mini",
  input: "Draft a refund response for this ticket"
});`;
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Outlayo | Usage-Based Spend Control</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Outlayo helps teams intercept usage, understand spend, and catch surprise bills before they hit runway."
    />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:opsz,wght@9..144,600;9..144,700&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style>
      :root {
        --ink: #12263a;
        --muted: #50657a;
        --surface: #fffdf8;
        --sand: #f4efe3;
        --accent: #0f766e;
        --accent-strong: #0d5f5a;
        --ring: rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.24);
        --shadow: 0 18px 45px rgba(18, 38, 58, 0.14);
        --font-body: "Space Grotesk", "Trebuchet MS", "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
        --font-display: "Fraunces", Georgia, serif;
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: var(--font-body);
        color: var(--ink);
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at 12% 18%, rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.2), transparent 42%),
          radial-gradient(circle at 88% 24%, rgba(14, 116, 144, 0.18), transparent 36%),
          linear-gradient(160deg, #fffdf8 0%, #f6f1e6 48%, #e9f8f4 100%);
        min-height: 100vh;
      }

      .landing-shell {
        max-width: 1100px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 22px 18px 40px;
      }

      .fade-up {
        animation: fadeUp 500ms ease-out both;
      }

      .fade-up.delay-1 {
        animation-delay: 120ms;
      }

      .fade-up.delay-2 {
        animation-delay: 220ms;
      }

      @keyframes fadeUp {
        from {
          opacity: 0;
          transform: translateY(14px);
        }

        to {
          opacity: 1;
          transform: translateY(0);
        }
      }

      .topbar {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(18, 38, 58, 0.12);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
        backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
        border-radius: 999px;
        padding: 10px 12px 10px 16px;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(18, 38, 58, 0.08);
      }

      .brand {
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      }

      .topbar-actions {
        display: flex;
        gap: 8px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        justify-content: flex-end;
      }

      .cta-btn {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 11px 18px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        border: 1px solid transparent;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: transform 160ms ease, box-shadow 160ms ease, background-color 160ms ease;
      }

      .cta-btn.primary {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent) 0%, #0a8794 100%);
        color: #ffffff;
        box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.32);
      }

      .cta-btn.secondary {
        border-color: rgba(18, 38, 58, 0.18);
        color: var(--ink);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.84);
      }

      .cta-btn:hover {
        transform: translateY(-1px);
      }

      .hero {
        margin-top: 18px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(18, 38, 58, 0.12);
        background: linear-gradient(140deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88), rgba(234, 251, 246, 0.82));
        border-radius: 28px;
        box-shadow: var(--shadow);
        padding: 30px;
        display: grid;
        gap: 28px;
        grid-template-columns: 1.25fr 0.95fr;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .hero::after {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        width: 220px;
        height: 220px;
        right: -60px;
        top: -60px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(14, 116, 144, 0.22), transparent 72%);
      }

      .eyebrow {
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.18em;
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--accent-strong);
      }

      .hero h1 {
        margin-top: 10px;
        margin-bottom: 0;
        font-family: var(--font-display);
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.6vw, 3.4rem);
        line-height: 1.05;
      }

      .hero p {
        margin-top: 14px;
        color: var(--muted);
        max-width: 45ch;
        font-size: 1.05rem;
      }

      .button-row {
        margin-top: 24px;
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 10px;
      }

      .hero-note {
        margin-top: 14px;
        font-size: 0.92rem;
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      .signal-card {
        border: 1px solid rgba(18, 38, 58, 0.12);
        border-radius: 18px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
        padding: 16px;
        z-index: 1;
      }

      .signal-card h2 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 0.96rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: #335067;
      }

      .signal-list {
        margin-top: 12px;
        display: grid;
        gap: 10px;
      }

      .signal-item {
        border-radius: 12px;
        background: var(--surface);
        border: 1px solid rgba(18, 38, 58, 0.1);
        padding: 10px 12px;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 8px;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }

      .signal-item strong {
        color: var(--accent-strong);
      }

      .cards {
        margin-top: 18px;
        display: grid;
        gap: 12px;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }

      .card {
        border-radius: 20px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(18, 38, 58, 0.12);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(18, 38, 58, 0.08);
        padding: 18px;
      }

      .card .kicker {
        font-size: 0.73rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.15em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: #335067;
      }

      .card h3 {
        margin-top: 6px;
        margin-bottom: 0;
        font-size: 1.06rem;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      .card p {
        margin-top: 6px;
        font-size: 0.94rem;
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      .proof {
        margin-top: 18px;
        border-radius: 20px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(18, 38, 58, 0.12);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
        padding: 20px;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(18, 38, 58, 0.08);
      }

      .proof h3 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      .proof-grid {
        margin-top: 12px;
        display: grid;
        gap: 10px;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }

      .pill {
        border-radius: 12px;
        background: linear-gradient(160deg, #ffffff, #f6fbfa);
        border: 1px solid rgba(18, 38, 58, 0.1);
        padding: 11px 12px;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: #27445a;
      }

      .install-demo {
        margin-top: 18px;
        border-radius: 22px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(18, 38, 58, 0.12);
        background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(18, 38, 58, 0.96), rgba(16, 30, 45, 0.94));
        color: #eef7f5;
        padding: 22px;
        box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(18, 38, 58, 0.16);
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 0.9fr 1.1fr;
        gap: 18px;
      }

      .install-demo h3 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      .install-demo p {
        margin-top: 8px;
        color: rgba(238, 247, 245, 0.76);
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        max-width: 36ch;
      }

      .demo-steps {
        margin-top: 14px;
        display: grid;
        gap: 10px;
      }

      .demo-step {
        border-radius: 14px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        padding: 10px 12px;
        font-size: 0.88rem;
        color: rgba(238, 247, 245, 0.9);
      }

      .demo-step code,
      .demo-code code {
        font-family: "SFMono-Regular", "SF Mono", Monaco, Consolas, "Liberation Mono", monospace;
      }

      .demo-code {
        border-radius: 18px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        background: rgba(6, 14, 23, 0.72);
        padding: 14px;
        overflow-x: auto;
      }

      .demo-code pre {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: "SFMono-Regular", "SF Mono", Monaco, Consolas, "Liberation Mono", monospace;
        font-size: 0.84rem;
        line-height: 1.55;
        color: #d9fbf1;
        white-space: pre;
      }

      .demo-label {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.18);
        border: 1px solid rgba(94, 234, 212, 0.2);
        color: #9ef3dd;
        font-size: 0.74rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.12em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        padding: 5px 9px;
      }

      .final-cta {
        margin-top: 18px;
        border-radius: 22px;
        border: 1px solid var(--ring);
        background: linear-gradient(140deg, rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.12), rgba(14, 116, 144, 0.1));
        padding: 24px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 12px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      .final-cta h4 {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: var(--font-display);
        font-size: 1.5rem;
      }

      .final-cta p {
        margin-top: 4px;
        color: #315167;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
      }

      .footer-note {
        margin-top: 16px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 0.78rem;
        color: #486276;
      }

      @media (max-width: 960px) {
        .hero {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .cards {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        }
      }

      @media (max-width: 640px) {
        .landing-shell {
          padding: 16px 14px 28px;
        }

        .hero {
          padding: 20px;
          border-radius: 24px;
        }

        .cards,
        .proof-grid,
        .install-demo {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .topbar {
          border-radius: 18px;
        }

        .final-cta {
          padding: 18px;
        }
      }

      @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
        .fade-up {
          animation: none;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="landing-shell">
      <header class="topbar fade-up">
        <div class="brand">Outlayo</div>
        <div class="topbar-actions">
          <a href="https://github.com/outlayo/outlayo" class="cta-btn secondary">Explore OSS</a>
          <a href="mailto:founders@outlayo.com?subject=Outlayo%20early%20access" class="cta-btn primary">Request access</a>
        </div>
      </header>

      <section class="hero fade-up delay-1">
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow">Usage-based spend control</p>
          <h1>Stop surprise usage bills before they hit your runway.</h1>
          <p>
            Outlayo intercepts app-side API usage, turns it into spend signals, and reconciles it with vendor data where trustworthy billing feeds exist.
          </p>
          <div class="button-row">
            <a id="early-access" href="mailto:founders@outlayo.com?subject=Outlayo%20early%20access" class="cta-btn primary">Request early access</a>
            <a href="https://github.com/outlayo/outlayo" class="cta-btn secondary">Explore the OSS repo</a>
          </div>
          <p class="hero-note">
            Built for startup founders, indie hackers, and infra-minded teams running OpenAI, cloud infra, and usage-priced APIs without a single source of truth.
          </p>
        </div>

        <aside class="signal-card">
          <h2>Signal Confidence</h2>
          <div class="signal-list">
            <div class="signal-item"><span>App-side usage interception</span><strong>Primary</strong></div>
            <div class="signal-item"><span>Authoritative vendor feeds</span><strong>Reconcile</strong></div>
            <div class="signal-item"><span>Confidence-aware spend model</span><strong>Tracked</strong></div>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </section>

      <section class="cards fade-up delay-2">
        <article class="card">
          <p class="kicker">Differentiator</p>
          <h3>Coverage without waiting on vendors</h3>
          <p>Intercept real application traffic first, so weak billing APIs do not block visibility.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <p class="kicker">Reconciliation</p>
          <h3>Authoritative where possible</h3>
          <p>Pull vendor telemetry where reliable feeds exist to reconcile estimates against stronger signals.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <p class="kicker">Action</p>
          <h3>Alert before margin slips</h3>
          <p>Forecast budget and free-tier breaches, then push webhook alerts before invoices turn into surprises.</p>
        </article>
      </section>

      <section class="proof fade-up delay-2">
        <h3>Why technical teams switch</h3>
        <div class="proof-grid">
          <div class="pill">One model for live usage, spend, and confidence</div>
          <div class="pill">Ingest-first coverage for real-world vendor gaps</div>
          <div class="pill">Preset extractors plus connector reconciliation</div>
          <div class="pill">Built-in export, dashboarding, and webhook automation</div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="oss" class="proof fade-up delay-2">
        <h3>Open Source + Hosted, clearly separated</h3>
        <div class="proof-grid">
          <div class="pill"><strong>OSS repo:</strong> connectors, core packages, docs, and contributor workflows</div>
          <div class="pill"><strong>Hosted app:</strong> managed service access at app.outlayo.com</div>
          <div class="pill"><strong>Public code:</strong> transparent runtime and integration logic</div>
          <div class="pill"><strong>Private ops:</strong> secrets, production infra state, abuse controls, tenant operations</div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="install-demo fade-up delay-2">
        <div>
          <span class="demo-label">Instrument in minutes</span>
          <h3>Show teams how little code it takes.</h3>
          <p>Add the ingest SDK, pass its tracked fetch into the client you already use, and start emitting usage events before you wire up any vendor reconciliation.</p>
          <div class="demo-steps">
            <div class="demo-step"><strong>1.</strong> Install <code>@outlayo/sdk-ingest</code> and add the OpenAI preset.</div>
            <div class="demo-step"><strong>2.</strong> Hand Outlayo's tracked <code>fetch</code> to your OpenAI client.</div>
            <div class="demo-step"><strong>3.</strong> Emit usage events to your Outlayo collector while connector reconciliation catches up later.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="demo-code">
          <span class="demo-label">Example</span>
          <pre><code>{instrumentationSnippet}</code></pre>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="final-cta fade-up delay-2">
        <div>
          <h4>Instrument one costly workflow this week.</h4>
          <p>Start with app-side interception, then layer in connector reconciliation where vendor telemetry is strong.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="mailto:founders@outlayo.com?subject=Outlayo%20early%20access" class="cta-btn primary">Request early access</a>
      </section>

      <footer class="footer-note">Built from the public repo. Updated at build time: {generatedAt}. Outlayo is currently in early access.</footer>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
